  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">• Full-scaled sandwich single-crystal molybdenum mirrors for H-alpha spectroscopy in ITER were manufactured. • The mirrors were thermally tested in vacuum camera in ITER-relevant conditions. • Bending of the mirrors were measured optically in-situ. • The bending observed did not exceed the tolerable limits.</subfield>
